column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.parentID, p.specObjID, p.ra, p.dec, s.z,s.zErr,s.zWarning,s.class, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z, p.flags, lnLExp_r,LnLDev_r, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.fracDev_r,p.expAB_r,p.expRad_r, g.h_alpha_eqw,g.sigma_balmer FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN galSpecLine as g ON g.SpecObjID = p.SpecobjID ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
